comments: Zubac (LAC) and James (LAL) mutually come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Russell (LAL) defends Harden's (LAC) drive and marginal contact occurs with Harden's (LAC) head on the play.
Davis's (LAL) foot makes incidental contact with the ball on the perimeter.
Russell (LAL) swipes for the ball as he contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with George's (LAC) arm.
Zubac (LAC) takes a step into Russell's (LAL) path and illegal contact occurs that affects his ability to defend over the pick.
George (LAC) moves alongside James' (LAL) path as he defends over the pick and marginal body contact occurs as the two come together.
Zubac (LAC) moves alongside James' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they engage during the driving shot attempt.
During the inbound, Powell (LAC) immediately slides his hand off of Prince's (LAL) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Mann (LAC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Harden (LAC) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Reaves' (LAL) arm during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Harden (LAC) commits a take foul on Prince (LAL).
Davis (LAL) is retreating his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs with Zubac's (LAC) off-arm during his post shot attempt.
George (LAC) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
Reaves (LAL) legally contests Powell's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
